Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:39.52,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我為了不讓其毀壞而太過於珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:45.44,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也輸入郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:51.31,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又將其刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.71,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這樣的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:56.88,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將其打破的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.72,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}為我帶來契機的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:04.70,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心將其緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.28,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將現在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.77,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}雖然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:15.64,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使將碎片全部收集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.84,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必須用自己的雙手將其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.54,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}極其珍視的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:24.89,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕將其失去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:30.58,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但是我所希望的這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.86,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}都存在於此
